WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.240
Home Alone Home Alone is a very funny 1990 American film.

00:08.240 --> 00:15.240
It tells a story about a boy who is accidentally left alone at home.

00:15.240 --> 00:20.560
One night before Christmas, the Macalester family meet at their home.

00:20.560 --> 00:25.760
They are planning to fly to Paris for the holiday and are busy getting ready.

00:25.800 --> 00:34.720
Eight-year-old Kevin is the youngest child and is fighting with his brothers and sisters and his cousins.

00:34.720 --> 00:42.960
When he goes to bed, he is so angry that he wishes all his family would go away.

00:42.960 --> 00:47.560
In the morning, everyone wakes up very late.

00:47.560 --> 00:53.320
They are all in a hurry to get to the airport, so they forget Kevin

00:53.360 --> 00:57.840
and he is left alone at home by accident.

00:57.840 --> 01:02.840
Although Kevin is alone, he is very happy at first.

01:02.840 --> 01:08.240
His terrible family has gone, his wish has come true.

01:08.240 --> 01:14.400
He watches TV, eats lots of fast food and plays games.

01:14.400 --> 01:17.160
He has a good time.

01:17.200 --> 01:24.040
But later on, he goes out and his two bad men called Harry and Marve

01:24.040 --> 01:27.640
planning to steal from his house.

01:27.640 --> 01:34.480
He goes home and plans some very funny ways to catch Harry and Marve.

01:34.480 --> 01:40.280
Many things in the house get broken as Kevin tries to stop them.

01:40.280 --> 01:45.240
Finally, the police come and the men are taken away.

01:45.280 --> 01:52.120
The house is now a mess, so Kevin tides it up and waits for his parents.

01:52.120 --> 01:58.600
They get back from Paris and are very happy to find that Kevin is safe.

